@{b}Version 2.2 June 1996@{ub}@{par}

 · Added @{" menupoint " link menu} to save eye position.@{par}
 · Negative values for BackColor are possible. This idea comes from Michael Hohmann. Thanks!@{par}

@{b}Version 2.1 May 1996@{ub}@{par}

 · added @{" ToolType " link ToolTypes} LowColor@{par}

@{b}Version 2.0 April 1996@{ub}@{par}

 · The eyes looking still to the mousepointer until the eyelid winks.@{par}
 · better calculation of pupil-position@{par}
 · the eyes are screwing if you go to the middle@{par}
 · BlueEyes now using CLI args@{par}
 · lower memory usage !@{par}
